
Install libraries manually:
---------------------------

Installation settings:

.. code-block:: bash

    source spectrocrunch/tools/linux/funcs.sh
    install_systemwide reset false
    dryrun reset false
    modify_bashrc reset false
    
Default source/build root directory (not necessary):

.. code-block:: bash

    source spectrocrunch/tools/linux/funcs-python.sh
    cd $(python_depdir)

Install any python version:

.. code-block:: bash

    source spectrocrunch/tools/linux/funcs-python.sh
    require_python 3.6

Install any gnu package:

.. code-block:: bash

    source spectrocrunch/tools/linux/funcs-glibc.sh
    require_gnu glibc 2.14

